{"id":883,"date":"2019-08-27T16:09:49","date_gmt":"2019-08-27T13:09:49","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/egepenakcayapi.com\/?p=883"},"modified":"2023-03-05T10:36:48","modified_gmt":"2023-03-05T07:36:48","slug":"kapi-gicirdamasi-nasil-giderilir-cozuldu","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/egepenakcayapi.com\/kapi-gicirdamasi-nasil-giderilir-cozuldu\/","title":{"rendered":"Kap\u0131 G\u0131c\u0131rt\u0131s\u0131 Nas\u0131l Giderilir? (\u00c7\u00d6Z\u00dcLD\u00dc)"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4721 alignleft\" src=\"https:\/\/egepenakcayapi.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/gicirti-300x290.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"370\" height=\"358\" srcset=\"https:\/\/egepenakcayapi.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/gicirti-300x290.jpg 300w, https:\/\/egepenakcayapi.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/gicirti.jpg 540w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 370px) 100vw, 370px\" \/><\/span><\/figure>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">\r\n\r\n<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">Kap\u0131lar mente\u015fe ve montaj yerlerinin belirli bir s\u00fcre sonra kullan\u0131m\u0131na ba\u011fl\u0131 olarak pas, toz vb. nedenlerle a\u015f\u0131nma yapar ve bazen sizi ve hatta bazen kom\u015fular\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 bile rahats\u0131z eden g\u0131c\u0131rt\u0131lar \u00e7\u0131karabilir. E\u011fer buna benzer k\u00fc\u00e7\u00fck ama rahats\u0131z eden sorunlar\u0131n\u0131z varsa i\u015fte \u00e7\u00f6z\u00fcm yolu<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">\r\n\r\n<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">En malum bilgi eskiden s\u00fcregelen makine ya\u011f\u0131d\u0131r. Sizlerde mente\u015felere k\u00fc\u00e7\u00fck damlalar halinde ya\u011f damlatarak ilk \u00e7\u00f6z\u00fcm\u00fc deneyebilirsiniz. Eskiden zeytinya\u011f\u0131 kullanarak kap\u0131 veya ah\u015fap g\u0131c\u0131rt\u0131lar\u0131n\u0131 gidermek de yayg\u0131n bir y\u00f6ntemdi. Her ne kadar bu y\u00f6ntem bug\u00fcn \u00e7ok hijyenik gibi durmasa da halen etkin bir \u00e7\u00f6z\u00fcm oldu\u011funu belirtmemizde fayda var. Nitekim do\u011fal olan her zaman do\u011fal \u00e7\u00f6z\u00fcmler getirir. Mum eriterek kap\u0131 aksesuarlar\u0131n\u0131 da ya\u011flamak m\u00fcmk\u00fcnd\u00fcr. Mumu eritip geri donmadan k\u00fc\u00e7\u00fck par\u00e7alar halinde kap\u0131 aksamlar\u0131na ve mente\u015fe oyuklar\u0131na s\u00fcrebilirsiniz. Bunun olduk\u00e7a etkili bir yol oldu\u011funu zamanla g\u00f6receksiniz.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">\r\n\r\n<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">Bula\u015f\u0131k deterjan\u0131 ile de kap\u0131 ya\u011flan\u0131r. Olur mu demeyin, ev han\u0131mlar\u0131n\u0131n s\u0131kl\u0131kla ba\u015fvurdu\u011fu bir yoldur. S\u00fcnger yard\u0131m\u0131yla bu i\u015flemi yap\u0131p etkilerini k\u0131sa s\u00fcrede g\u00f6receksiniz. Yine ayn\u0131 \u015fekilde vazelin, gres ya\u011f\u0131, bebek ya\u011f\u0131 vb. s\u0131v\u0131larla ya\u011flama yapabilirsiniz.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">\r\n\r\n<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">\u00d6NEML\u0130 NOT: Pas ve ya\u011f s\u00f6k\u00fcc\u00fc veya \u00e7\u00f6z\u00fcc\u00fc spreylerde zaman zaman g\u0131c\u0131rt\u0131 gidermede kullan\u0131l\u0131yor ancak unutmay\u0131n\u0131z a\u015f\u0131r\u0131 kimyasal i\u00e7eren bu maddeleri dikkatli kullanmal\u0131s\u0131n\u0131z. Zira hem size hem de aile bireylerine \u00f6zellikle de bebeklere olumsuz etkisi \u00e7ok fazla.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">\r\n\r\n<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">T\u00fcm bunlar\u0131 denediniz ama yine g\u0131c\u0131rt\u0131 sorunu d\u00fczelmedi. O zaman kap\u0131n\u0131z\u0131n oturdu\u011fu zeminde veya kap\u0131n\u0131n \u00fcst kiri\u015finde binan\u0131n zamanla yerine oturmas\u0131ndan kaynakl\u0131 bas\u0131kl\u0131klar ve s\u0131k\u0131\u015f\u0131kl\u0131klar var demektir. Bu profesyonel bir i\u015f\u00e7ilik gerektirir ve in\u015faat-do\u011frama aln\u0131na girer.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">\r\n\r\n<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">E\u011fer b\u00f6yle bir tespitiniz olmas\u0131 halinde EgepenAk\u00e7ayap\u0131 \u2013 \u0130\u00e7 ve D\u0131\u015f Yap\u0131 Dekorasyon bizimle a\u015fa\u011f\u0131daki <a title=\"\u0130LET\u0130\u015e\u0130M\" href=\"https:\/\/egepenakcayapi.com\/iletisim-egepenakcayapi-kimdir\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ileti\u015fim<\/a> bilgilerinden ileti\u015fime ge\u00e7ebilir, deneyimli ustalar\u0131m\u0131zdan teknik destek alabilir veya i\u015f yerimize gelerek se\u00e7enekleri birlikte de\u011ferlendirebiliriz.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;\">\r\n\r\n<\/span><\/p>